{{Top|leg}}
An '''automixer''' or '''automix machine'''<ref name="CD">{{JournalCite|1|Chessa's Doom}}</ref> was a vending device used in [[Cantina/Legends|cantinas]] and clubs all over the [[Galaxy/Legends|galaxy]]. Those who used it would choose their [[Species/Legends|species]] and the automixer would provide them with an appropriate beverage. This prevented patrons from becoming poisoned due to drinking a beverage that might have been [[Poison|toxic]] to their species.

